snippet.title: The First Tree - Mobile Trailer
snippet.description:
The award-winning exploration game is finally available on iOS and Android devices! Coming November 18th, 2020. Store links below:

App Store link: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/the-first-tree/id1524841987
Google Play link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.davidwehle.thefirsttree
Website: http://www.thefirsttree.com/
